PetaVision is an open source, object oriented neural simulation toolbox optimized for high-performance multi-core, multi-node computer architectures.

Quick instructions for installing PetaVision and running the system tests:

git clone https://github.com/PetaVision/openpv
cd openpv
echo PVSystemTests > subdirectories.txt
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug
make
cd PVSystemTests
ctest

We are currently in the process of migrating from SourceForge to GitHub.  Our webpage on SourceForge is <http://petavision.sourceforge.net>.  Our webpage on GitHub is <http://petavision.github.io/>.

Currently (Aug 7, 2015), the SourceForge website is more complete but it will not be further updated; the GitHub website will be completed soon.
